# MCP Servers Configuration (Optional)
# MCP servers are configured using mcp.json files (Cursor format)
# 
# Project-level config: .cursor/mcp.json (in project root)
# Global config: ~/.cursor/mcp.json (in home directory)
#
# See .cursor/mcp.json.example for configuration examples
#
# Supported configuration interpolation:
# - ${env:NAME} - Environment variables
# - ${userHome} - User home directory
# - ${workspaceFolder} - Project root directory
# - ${workspaceFolderBasename} - Project root directory name
# - ${pathSeparator} or ${/} - OS path separator
